---
title: Honey-Mustard Pork Chops with Roasted Potatoes and Green Beans
description: A savoury honey dressing acts as a zippy flavour booster for pork chops in this no-fuss recipe. Paired with blistered green beans and roasted potatoes, it's the ultimate dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelettes-de-porc-au-miel-et-a-la-moutarde-15978362.jpg
